[{"question":"Who has the thickest skin, you or the rhino?","answer":"Well, I don\u0027t know.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":44,"aSentId":45},{"question":"How long is that going to last, do you think?","answer":"INGRICH: I don\u0027t know, but I thought it was a very good sign.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":55,"aSentId":56},{"question":"-- it is a -- it is a radical -- but it is a radical form of social engineering, isn\u0027t it?","answer":"But -- well, but the current Ryan plan, which he developed with Senator Ron Wyden, a Democrat, the only bipartisan plan to save Medicare.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":80,"aSentId":81},{"question":"As a Catholic, what is your reaction?","answer":"Well, first of all, I would encourage everybody who\u0027s concerned about Catholic social doctrine to read Paul Ryan\u0027s remarkable speech at Georgetown in which he outlines his commitment to precisely the concerns of the church and helping the poor.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":103,"aSentId":104},{"question":"How would you describe that?","answer":"Wait -- wait a second, Piers.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":152,"aSentId":153},{"question":"No?","answer":"Ronald Reagan had a deeper recession under Jimmy Carter and Ronald Reagan recovered in three years.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":164,"aSentId":165},{"question":"And I guess more importantly, what do you think about the guy who did get the gig?","answer":"AWLENTY: I think it\u0027s a terrific pick.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":187,"aSentId":188},{"question":"When you are being vetted, I mean -- how many years back do you have to go in the vetting process?","answer":"Well, Governor Romney has committed to release two years of tax returns.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":196,"aSentId":197},{"question":"I mean unless you\u0027ve got something to hide, why wouldn\u0027t you?","answer":"I think his position\u0027s very reasonable, Piers, for this.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":202,"aSentId":203},{"question":"If you were a guessing man, what percentage of the Ryan budget plan could you envisage a Romney presidency actually adopting?","answer":"Well, Governor Romney has said he\u0027s going to have his own plan and does have his own plan.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":216,"aSentId":217},{"question":"Secretary of state maybe?","answer":"You just don\u0027t quit.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":241,"aSentId":242},{"question":"But what is the Democrat view of the hyperbole that\u0027s now surrounding this guy?","answer":"Well, clearly, Piers, he\u0027s energizing the Republican Tea Party base.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":271,"aSentId":272},{"question":"There\u0027s now a clear ideological difference for American people to vote on come November, isn\u0027t there?","answer":"Well, there is.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":282,"aSentId":283},{"question":"How does the American voter cut through all this and actually come to a clear verdict on this plan, giving that he\u0027s now going to be the VP running mate?","answer":"Well, Piers, I think they should first go and look at the plan and they should also look at the Democratic budget committee analysis of the plan.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":299,"aSentId":300},{"question":"It\u0027s just how we get there, right?","answer":"Well, absolutely.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":319,"aSentId":320},{"question":"Was I reading the ruins correctly?","answer":"Well, I think there\u0027s some of that.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":338,"aSentId":339},{"question":"How you doing?","answer":"Welcome, sir.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":401,"aSentId":402},{"question":"You finally got me, huh?","answer":"It\u0027s taken me nearly two years.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":403,"aSentId":404},{"question":"-- than it has been, 20 years ago, in your experience, since you began making movies?","answer":"I think that it\u0027s that whole thing, one step forward, one step back.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":451,"aSentId":452},{"question":"What did you say?","answer":"I said people thought he was Jesus.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":474,"aSentId":475},{"question":"Where do you think if he gets re-elected he should push harder?","answer":"The bottom line is economics.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":496,"aSentId":497},{"question":"Did you like the Olympics?","answer":"Say it again.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":533,"aSentId":534},{"question":"Did you like the Olympics?","answer":"Oh, yeah.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":535,"aSentId":536},{"question":"You don\u0027t see I\u0027m wearing my jacket?","answer":"I do.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":537,"aSentId":538},{"question":"Wasn\u0027t bad, was it?","answer":"You guys did great.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":543,"aSentId":544},{"question":"But has it made America more or less racist?","answer":"I like to say, first of all, African-Americans alone did not elect President Obama.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":548,"aSentId":549},{"question":"Where?","answer":"It was down in Texas I think.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":565,"aSentId":566},{"question":"How many people die of gunshots in England every year?","answer":"This is the point I make.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":574,"aSentId":575},{"question":"The guy from Aurora, how can you buy that much ammunition on the Internet and that\u0027s not a red flag?","answer":"There were never red flags.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":586,"aSentId":587},{"question":"Well what do you do about NRA, which holds this incredible power?","answer":"They got the -- the Vulcan death grip.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":597,"aSentId":598},{"question":"Should -- should Barack Obama, rather than just talk in this kind of slightly rhetoric way, as he does about guns, should he now push?","answer":"I think they both should.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":603,"aSentId":604},{"question":"And then gone, how do you feel about it?","answer":"I\u0027m over it now, but I -- it came out of nowhere.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":651,"aSentId":652},{"question":"How are you going to feel when he comes to the Garden in a Houston shirt?","answer":"Well, he\u0027s got to have to come down the lane.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":661,"aSentId":662},{"question":"Hey, I\u0027m not -- no blood, no foul, right?","answer":"You just finished doing the Mike Tyson Show, which I saw a fledgling version of it in Vegas.","docId":"120813pmt","qSentId":664,"aSentId":665}]